        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，且住！此书是我出自心裁，怎么又与古人同心，莫非我梦得古书不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了！既有此书，要它何用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将此书用火焚化，并令各班部，凡有此书，一概焚毁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我视张松形容古怪，出言猖狂，有些自大。我不轻视于他，他必然藐视于我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日也不用他拜见，以待明日清晨，将文武官员，调齐教场，命他在教场拜见，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一来叫他看看我的威严，二来要他回转西蜀，告与刘璋。此意如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨修",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相爷高见，卑职告退。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓谕张松。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨修",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨修",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领了丞相命，告知有才人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨修下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿我令箭，晓谕文武各班，明日清晨，文穿补服，武披铠甲，各带人马，教场"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相有令：明日清晨，文穿补服，武披铠甲，各带人马，教场伺候！"
        }
      ],
